# ${code} : ${name}

Personal archive of course material from **${name}** (${code}, ${term}), extracted from Canvas LMS via the [canvas-archive](https://github.com/cruzaddy91/canvas-archive) tool.

## Contents

Course material authored or posted by the instructor: slides, assignment prompts, lecture pages, modules, files, and quiz metadata.

**Excluded by design:** submissions, grades, syllabus, roster, announcements, discussions.

## Provenance

- Canvas course id: `${canvas_id}`
- Term: `${term}`
- Initial archive: `${archived_at}`

This repository is private and intended for personal reference only. Course material remains the intellectual property of its authors.
